% a PDF file showing how names tree can make it possible to split a script.
% moreover, unlike /OpenAction, the trigger is not obvious in this case.

% BSD Licence, Ange Albertini, 2011

%PDF-1.

1 0 obj
<<
/Kids
  [<<
  /Parent 1 0 R
  >>]
>>

trailer
<<
/Root
  <<
  /Pages 1 0 R
  /Names
    <<
    /JavaScript
       <<
       /Names[
            (1) <<
                /S /JavaScript
                /JS(
                  msg = "Hello";
                  )
              >>
            (2) <<
                /S /JavaScript
                /JS(
                  msg = msg + " World!";
                  app.alert(msg);
                  )
              >>
           ]
       >>
    >>
  >>
>>